parsermigration-edit-subtitle: A subtitle shown below the h1 when editing a page with the tool
parsermigration-current:
Adjective. The column heading for the article HTML as shown by the current parser.
{{Identical|Current}}
parsermigration-new:
The column heading for the article HTML as shown by the "new" parser
{{Identical|New}}
parsermigration-pref-label: The user preference label for a checkbox which enables the feature
parsermigration-pref-help: Help text for the user preference checkbox
parsermigration-toolbox-label: The text of the toolbox link, which allows the user to edit the page with a special user interface.
parsermigration-parsoid-readviews-select: The user preference label for drop-down selector which allows opt-in, opt-out, or the use of the wiki default setting for the use of the new Parsoid parser
Help text for the user preference drop-down selector for the use of the new Parsoid parser
parsermigration-parsoid-readviews-always: Selector text used when the user wants to always use the new Parsoid parser to render wikitext
parsermigration-parsoid-readviews-defaul: Selector text used when the user wants to follow the wiki default preferences for the use of the Parsoid parser to render wikitext
parsermigration-parsoid-readviews-never: Selector text used when the user wants to never use the new Parsoid parser to render wikitext
parsermigration-use-legacy-parser-toolbo: The text of the toolbox link which allows the user to use the legacy parser to render this page
parsermigration-use-parsoid-toolbox-labe: The text of the toolbox link which allows the user to use the Parsoid parser to render this page
parsermigration-report-bug-toolbox-label: The text of the toolbox link that allows the user to report a visual bug with the rendering of the page
parsermigration-report-bug-toolbox-title: The tool tip for the toolbox link that allows the user to report a visual bug with the rendering of the page
parsermigration-notice-title: Title text for a notification displayed when a user views a page rendered with the Parsoid wikitext parser for the first time.
parsermigration-notice-body: Body text for a notification displayed when a user views a page rendered with the Parsoid wikitext parser for the first time.
parsermigration-parsoid-chip-label: Short text for an indicator at the top of a main space page marking a page that has been rendered with the new Parsoid wikitext parser.
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-cancel-:
Label for the button which closes the "Report Visual Bug" dialog
{{Identical|Cancel}}
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-complet:
Thanks message, appears if submission of the report was successful. Parameters:
* $1 - Feedback page title
* $2 - Feedback page URL

The title of the "Report Visual Bug" dialog after successful submission of the report
{{Identical|Thank you}}
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-desc: Descriptive text at the top of the dialog box for "Report Visual Bug" feature
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-destina:
Description of the page where the message created by the "Report Visual Bug" dialog will be posted. Parameters:
* $1 - Feedback page title
* $2 - Feedback page URL
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-done-bu:
Label for the button which closes the "Report Visual Bug" dialog upon successful submission of the report
{{Identical|Done}}
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-error-l: Label for the error message shown when the report can not be submitted
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-message:
Label for the text field showing the body of the message created by the "Report Visual Bug" dialog; this also shows the current page and revision. Parameters:
* $1 - Current page title
* $2 - Current page revision
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-placeho: Placeholder text in the "Report Visual Bug" dialog
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-progres: Label for the progress spinner after submission of a report
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-retry-b:
Label for the button which submits the "Report Visual Bug" dialog after an error
{{Identical|Retry}}
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-submit-:
Label for the button which submits the "Report Visual Bug" dialog
{{Identical|Submit}}
parsermigration-reportbug-dialog-title: Title of the dialog box for "Report Visual Bug" feature
parsermigration-reportbug-feedback-title:
{{Optional}}
A title of a page on a local wiki where users can leave feedback using the "Report Visual Bug" feature. (This feature is not necessarily enabled; depending on the wiki's configuration, the issues may also be reported to a page on a central wiki in a wiki family.)
tag-parsermigration-visual-bug: Change tag for reports created by the "Report Visual Bug" feature
